{"tid":988864,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"世上最可愛松鼠狗Boo睡夢中離世　享年13歲😭","createTime":"2019-01-20T12:31:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-21T08:40:46.000Z","uid":294,"like":8,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"99a8bf34ed04f3a1abd1a6133a92b64fcc558f9d","tid":988864,"uid":294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T12:31:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZWZXp1n.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZWZXp1n.png&h=b7b5f165&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n說起松鼠狗，相信大家都認識這隻松鼠狗Boo，牠的樣子甜美、可愛，早前更有網友都把牠封為「世界最可愛的松鼠狗」。<br />\n可惜，Boo的主人今早（1月19日）在牠的Facebook發文表示，Boo在睡夢中離世。<br />\n<br />\nBoo的主人今早（1月19日）在Facebook發文指，Boo已經在睡夢中離世：「Boo今天早上在牠睡夢中離世，我們感到傷心欲絕，但我們同時因為牠不再感到痛苦和不適而感到安慰。我們知道Buddy會是第一個在彩虹橋另一端迎接牠的狗狗。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/91WfbHg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F91WfbHg.png&h=6db80090&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"064ac1536de14c32a64ccb2a85bbdda726d1d882","tid":988864,"uid":294,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T12:31:55.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/-ePGMfDkTHo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F-ePGMfDkTHo&d=jaV%2BRe3y%2FXUob74I7FcGrDPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=77dac7f4\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/-ePGMfDkTHo</a>"},{"pid":"cfc3524fdbe329cb7a204c66441c7d20d6f3bddc","tid":988864,"uid":34572,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T12:31:57.000Z","msg":"OK仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"215d59d7ad9ebdd48641d616a3e428a03fb41dc1","tid":988864,"uid":294,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cfc3524fdbe329cb7a204c66441c7d20d6